{
    "publish_date": "2014-12-01T18:45:27.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT17M23S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "I grew up with my identical twin,", 
            "dur": "2.607", 
            "start": "9.034"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "who was an incredibly loving brother.", 
            "dur": "3.318", 
            "start": "12.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now, one thing about being a twin\nis it makes you an expert", 
            "dur": "4.181", 
            "start": "15.374"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "at spotting favoritism.", 
            "dur": "2.087", 
            "start": "20.053"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If his cookie was even slightly bigger\nthan my cookie, I had questions.", 
            "dur": "5.722", 
            "start": "22.778"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And clearly I wasn&#39;t starving.", 
            "dur": "2.471", 
            "start": "28.8"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "2.671", 
            "start": "32.564"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When I became a psychologist,", 
            "dur": "2.125", 
            "start": "35.235"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I began to notice favoritism\nof a different kind.", 
            "dur": "3.074", 
            "start": "37.36"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that is how much more\nwe value the body than we do the mind.", 
            "dur": "4.671", 
            "start": "41.146"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I spent nine years at University\nearning my doctorate in Psychology,", 
            "dur": "5.165", 
            "start": "46.283"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I can&#39;t tell you how many people\nlook at my business card and say,", 
            "dur": "4.214", 
            "start": "52.34"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Oh, a psychologist,\nso not a real doctor.&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.929", 
            "start": "56.554"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As if it should say that on my card.", 
            "dur": "2.676", 
            "start": "62.778"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "2.806", 
            "start": "65.501"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This favoritism we show\nthe body over the mind,", 
            "dur": "4.249", 
            "start": "69.372"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I see it everywhere.\n", 
            "dur": "1.796", 
            "start": "73.621"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I recently was at a friends&#39; house,", 
            "dur": "2.386", 
            "start": "75.691"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and their five-year-old\nwas getting ready for bed.", 
            "dur": "2.482", 
            "start": "78.077"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He was standing on a stool\nby the sink brushing his teeth,", 
            "dur": "3.423", 
            "start": "80.559"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when he slipped, and scratched his leg\non the stool when he fell.", 
            "dur": "3.679", 
            "start": "83.982"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He cried for a minute,\nbut then he got back up,", 
            "dur": "2.923", 
            "start": "87.874"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "got back on the stool\nand reached out for a box of Band-Aids", 
            "dur": "3.946", 
            "start": "90.797"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to put one on his cut.", 
            "dur": "2.513", 
            "start": "94.743"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now this kid could barely\ntie his shoelaces,", 
            "dur": "3.819", 
            "start": "97.573"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but he knew you have to cover a cut,\nso it doesn&#39;t become infected,", 
            "dur": "4.198", 
            "start": "101.392"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you have to care for your teeth\nby brushing twice a day.", 
            "dur": "3.835", 
            "start": "105.59"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We all know how to maintain\nour physical health", 
            "dur": "3.18", 
            "start": "109.425"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and how to practice dental hygiene, right?", 
            "dur": "3.053", 
            "start": "112.605"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We&#39;ve known it\nsince we were five years old.", 
            "dur": "3.34", 
            "start": "115.658"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But what do we know about maintaining\nour psychological health?", 
            "dur": "4.907", 
            "start": "118.998"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, nothing.", 
            "dur": "2.122", 
            "start": "124.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What do we teach our children\nabout emotional hygiene?", 
            "dur": "3.39", 
            "start": "126.178"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Nothing.", 
            "dur": "1.482", 
            "start": "130.92"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "How is it we spend more time", 
            "dur": "2.672", 
            "start": "132.967"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "taking care our teeth\nthan we do our minds?", 
            "dur": "3.448", 
            "start": "135.639"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Why is it our physical health\nis so much more important to us", 
            "dur": "4.377", 
            "start": "140.385"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "than our psychological health?", 
            "dur": "2.837", 
            "start": "144.762"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You know we sustain psychological injuries\n\n", 
            "dur": "2.79", 
            "start": "147.913"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "even more often than we do physical ones.", 
            "dur": "2.546", 
            "start": "150.703"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Injuries like failure or rejection,\nor loneliness,", 
            "dur": "3.681", 
            "start": "153.249"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and they can also\nget worse if we ignore them.", 
            "dur": "2.874", 
            "start": "156.93"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And they can impact our lives\nin dramatic ways.", 
            "dur": "3.211", 
            "start": "160.055"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And yet, even though there are\nscientifically proven techniques", 
            "dur": "4.484", 
            "start": "163.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we could use to treat these kinds\nof psychological injuries, we don&#39;t.", 
            "dur": "4.906", 
            "start": "167.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It doesn&#39;t even occur to us\nthat we should.", 
            "dur": "3.338", 
            "start": "173.377"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Oh, you&#39;re feeling depressed,\njust shake it off, it&#39;s all in your head.&quot;", 
            "dur": "4.551", 
            "start": "176.966"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Can you imagine saying that\nto somebody with a broken leg,", 
            "dur": "3.038", 
            "start": "181.517"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Just walk it off, it&#39;s all in your leg.&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.204", 
            "start": "184.555"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "2.249", 
            "start": "187.759"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It is time we close the gap between\nour physical and our psychological health.", 
            "dur": "5.2", 
            "start": "190.008"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s time we made them more equal.", 
            "dur": "3.039", 
            "start": "195.271"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "More like twins.", 
            "dur": "2.203", 
            "start": "198.31"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Speaking of which,\nmy brother is also a psychologist.", 
            "dur": "3.65", 
            "start": "201.349"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So he&#39;s not a real doctor, either.", 
            "dur": "3.083", 
            "start": "205.013"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.856", 
            "start": "208.096"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We didn&#39;t study together, though.", 
            "dur": "2.011", 
            "start": "209.952"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In fact, the hardest thing I&#39;ve ever done\nin my life", 
            "dur": "3.859", 
            "start": "211.963"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is move across the Atlantic\nto New York city", 
            "dur": "2.822", 
            "start": "216.19"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to get my doctorate in psychology.", 
            "dur": "2.744", 
            "start": "219.012"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We were apart then,\nfor the first time in our lives,", 
            "dur": "2.934", 
            "start": "221.756"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the separation\nwas brutal for both of us.", 
            "dur": "3.381", 
            "start": "224.69"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But while he remained\namong family and friends,", 
            "dur": "3.095", 
            "start": "228.447"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was alone in a new country.", 
            "dur": "2.643", 
            "start": "231.542"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We missed each other terribly,", 
            "dur": "2.268", 
            "start": "234.185"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but international phone calls\nwere really expensive then,", 
            "dur": "3.02", 
            "start": "236.453"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and we could only afford\nto speak for 5 minutes a week.", 
            "dur": "4.305", 
            "start": "239.473"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When our birthday rolled around,", 
            "dur": "1.718", 
            "start": "244.738"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it was the first\nwe wouldn&#39;t be spending together,", 
            "dur": "2.37", 
            "start": "246.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we decide to splurge,", 
            "dur": "1.39", 
            "start": "248.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that week\nwe would talk for ten minutes.", 
            "dur": "3.359", 
            "start": "250.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I spent the morning pacing around my room,", 
            "dur": "2.675", 
            "start": "253.575"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "waiting for him to call,", 
            "dur": "1.793", 
            "start": "256.25"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and waiting,", 
            "dur": "1.728", 
            "start": "258.043"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and waiting,", 
            "dur": "1.63", 
            "start": "260.415"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but the phone didn&#39;t ring.", 
            "dur": "1.94", 
            "start": "262.045"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Given the time difference, I assumed", 
            "dur": "2.151", 
            "start": "263.985"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;OK, he&#39;s out with friends,\nhe will call later.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.672", 
            "start": "266.136"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There were no cell phones then.", 
            "dur": "2.648", 
            "start": "268.808"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But he didn&#39;t.", 
            "dur": "1.815", 
            "start": "271.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I began to realize,\nafter being away for over ten months,", 
            "dur": "4.811", 
            "start": "273.271"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "he no longer missed me\nthe way I missed him.", 
            "dur": "3.339", 
            "start": "278.082"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I knew he would call in the morning,", 
            "dur": "2.352", 
            "start": "282.173"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but that night was one of the saddest\nand longest nights of my life.", 
            "dur": "5.077", 
            "start": "284.525"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I woke up the next morning,", 
            "dur": "2.098", 
            "start": "290.58"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I glanced down at the phone,", 
            "dur": "2.196", 
            "start": "292.678"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I realized\nI had kicked it off the hook", 
            "dur": "2.747", 
            "start": "294.874"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when pacing the day before.", 
            "dur": "2.338", 
            "start": "297.621"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I stumbled out of bed,", 
            "dur": "1.807", 
            "start": "300.85"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I put the phone\nback on the receiver,", 
            "dur": "1.771", 
            "start": "302.657"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and it rang a second later,", 
            "dur": "1.584", 
            "start": "304.428"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and it was my brother,\nand, boy, was he pissed.", 
            "dur": "3.319", 
            "start": "306.012"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "2.197", 
            "start": "309.331"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was the saddest and longest \nnight of his life as well.", 
            "dur": "3.44", 
            "start": "311.528"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I tried to explain what happened,\nbut he said,", 
            "dur": "2.592", 
            "start": "314.968"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;I don&#39;t understand,\nif you saw I wasn&#39;t calling you,", 
            "dur": "3.09", 
            "start": "317.56"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "why didn&#39;t you just pick up the phone\nand call me?&quot;", 
            "dur": "4.174", 
            "start": "320.718"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He was right.", 
            "dur": "1.632", 
            "start": "325.399"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Why didn&#39;t I call him?", 
            "dur": "2.007", 
            "start": "327.031"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I didn&#39;t have an answer then,\nbut I do today, and it&#39;s a simple one.", 
            "dur": "5.121", 
            "start": "329.397"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Loneliness.", 
            "dur": "2.113", 
            "start": "335.298"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Loneliness creates\na deep psychological wound.", 
            "dur": "3.844", 
            "start": "338.082"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "One that distorts our perceptions", 
            "dur": "2.156", 
            "start": "342.069"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and scrambles our thinking,", 
            "dur": "2.427", 
            "start": "344.225"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It makes us believe", 
            "dur": "1.35", 
            "start": "346.652"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "those around us care much less\nthan they actually do.", 
            "dur": "3.89", 
            "start": "348.002"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It makes us really afraid to reach out,", 
            "dur": "2.584", 
            "start": "351.892"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because why set yourself up\nfor rejection and heartache,", 
            "dur": "4.137", 
            "start": "354.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when your heart is already aching\nmore than you can stand?", 
            "dur": "3.655", 
            "start": "358.613"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was in the grips of real loneliness\nback then,", 
            "dur": "3.065", 
            "start": "362.473"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I was surrounded by people all day,", 
            "dur": "2.665", 
            "start": "365.538"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so it never occurred to me.", 
            "dur": "2.142", 
            "start": "368.203"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But loneliness, is defined purely,\nsubjectively.", 
            "dur": "3.706", 
            "start": "370.345"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It depends solely on whether you feel", 
            "dur": "3.275", 
            "start": "374.657"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "emotionally or socially disconnected\nfrom those around you.", 
            "dur": "3.483", 
            "start": "377.932"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I did.", 
            "dur": "1.811", 
            "start": "381.415"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There&#39;s a lot research on loneliness\n", 
            "dur": "2.633", 
            "start": "383.689"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and all of it is horrifying.", 
            "dur": "2.5", 
            "start": "386.322"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Loneliness won&#39;t just make you miserable,\nit will kill you.", 
            "dur": "4.265", 
            "start": "389.863"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I am not kidding.", 
            "dur": "1.324", 
            "start": "394.139"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Chronic loneliness increases your\nlikelihood of an early death", 
            "dur": "3.224", 
            "start": "395.463"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "by 14 percent.", 
            "dur": "2.105", 
            "start": "398.687"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Fourteen percent.", 
            "dur": "1.811", 
            "start": "401.102"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Loneliness causes high blood pressure,\nhigh cholesterol,", 
            "dur": "3.682", 
            "start": "403.074"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it even suppresses\nthe functioning of your immune system,", 
            "dur": "3.683", 
            "start": "406.876"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "making you vulnerable to all kinds\nof illnesses and diseases.", 
            "dur": "4.057", 
            "start": "410.615"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In fact, scientist have concluded\nthat taken together,", 
            "dur": "3.495", 
            "start": "414.672"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "chronic loneliness poses\na significant a risk", 
            "dur": "3.823", 
            "start": "418.167"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for your longterm health and longevity\nas cigarette smoking.", 
            "dur": "4.498", 
            "start": "421.99"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now, cigarette packs come with warnings\nsaying, &quot;This could kill you.&quot;", 
            "dur": "4.07", 
            "start": "426.991"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But loneliness doesn&#39;t.", 
            "dur": "2.187", 
            "start": "431.103"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that&#39;s why it&#39;s so important", 
            "dur": "1.942", 
            "start": "433.29"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we prioritize our psychological health.", 
            "dur": "3.332", 
            "start": "435.232"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That we practice emotional hygiene.", 
            "dur": "2.88", 
            "start": "438.564"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because you can&#39;t treat\na psychological wound", 
            "dur": "2.715", 
            "start": "441.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if you don&#39;t even know you are injured.", 
            "dur": "2.122", 
            "start": "444.611"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[Pay attention to emotional pain]", 
            "dur": "2.073", 
            "start": "446.733"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Loneliness isn&#39;t the only\npsychological wound", 
            "dur": "2.497", 
            "start": "448.806"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that distorts our perceptions\nand misleads us.", 
            "dur": "2.875", 
            "start": "451.303"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[Failure]", 
            "dur": "1.528", 
            "start": "454.185"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Failure does that as well.", 
            "dur": "2.415", 
            "start": "455.713"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I once visited a daycare center\nwhere I saw three toddlers", 
            "dur": "3.982", 
            "start": "458.128"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "play with identical plastic toys.", 
            "dur": "2.672", 
            "start": "462.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You had to slide the red button,\nand a cute doggy would pop out.", 
            "dur": "4.308", 
            "start": "465.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "One little girl tried pulling\nthe purple button, then pushing it,", 
            "dur": "4.63", 
            "start": "469.905"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and then she just sat back\nand looked at the box", 
            "dur": "2.823", 
            "start": "474.535"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with her lower lip trembling.", 
            "dur": "2.092", 
            "start": "477.358"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The little boy next to her,\nwatched this happen,", 
            "dur": "2.896", 
            "start": "479.45"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "then turned to his box,\nand burst into tears", 
            "dur": "2.44", 
            "start": "482.346"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "without even touching it.", 
            "dur": "2.053", 
            "start": "484.786"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Meanwhile, another little girl\ntried everything she could think of", 
            "dur": "3.646", 
            "start": "487.132"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "until she slid the red button,", 
            "dur": "1.969", 
            "start": "490.778"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the cute doggy popped out,\nand she squealed with delight.", 
            "dur": "4.682", 
            "start": "492.747"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So three toddlers\nwith identical plastic toys", 
            "dur": "3.19", 
            "start": "497.429"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but with very different\nreactions to failure.", 
            "dur": "2.99", 
            "start": "500.619"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The first two toddlers were perfectly\ncapable of sliding a red button.", 
            "dur": "4.241", 
            "start": "504.227"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The only thing that prevented them\nfrom succeeding", 
            "dur": "3.16", 
            "start": "509.016"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "was their mind tricked them\ninto believing they could not.", 
            "dur": "4.297", 
            "start": "512.176"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now, adults get tricked this way\nas well all the time.", 
            "dur": "4.126", 
            "start": "516.473"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In fact we all have a default set\nof feelings and beliefs", 
            "dur": "4.483", 
            "start": "520.97"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that gets triggered whenever\nwe encounter frustrations and setbacks.", 
            "dur": "4.196", 
            "start": "525.828"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Are you aware of how\nyour mind reacts to failure?", 
            "dur": "3.144", 
            "start": "530.024"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You need to be.", 
            "dur": "1.472", 
            "start": "533.418"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because if your mind tries to convince you", 
            "dur": "2.593", 
            "start": "534.89"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you&#39;re incapable of something", 
            "dur": "1.807", 
            "start": "537.483"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you believe it,", 
            "dur": "1.48", 
            "start": "539.29"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "then like those two toddlers,\nyou&#39;ll begin to feel helpless,", 
            "dur": "3.36", 
            "start": "540.77"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you&#39;ll stop trying too soon\nor you won&#39;t even try at all.", 
            "dur": "3.764", 
            "start": "544.13"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then you will be even more convinced\nyou can&#39;t succeed.", 
            "dur": "3.723", 
            "start": "547.894"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You see, that&#39;s why so many people", 
            "dur": "1.711", 
            "start": "551.617"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "function below their actual potential.", 
            "dur": "2.537", 
            "start": "553.328"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because somewhere along the way,\nsometimes a single failure", 
            "dur": "3.484", 
            "start": "555.865"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "convinced them they couldn&#39;t succeed,", 
            "dur": "2.54", 
            "start": "559.349"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and they believed it.", 
            "dur": "1.59", 
            "start": "561.893"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Once we become convinced of something,", 
            "dur": "2.533", 
            "start": "563.483"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s very difficult to change our mind.", 
            "dur": "2.61", 
            "start": "566.016"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I learned that lesson the hard way.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "568.626"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When I was a teenager with my brother.", 
            "dur": "2.275", 
            "start": "570.626"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We were driving with friends\ndown a dark road at night,", 
            "dur": "3.609", 
            "start": "572.901"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when the police car stopped us.", 
            "dur": "1.752", 
            "start": "576.51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There had been a robbery in the area,\nthey were looking for suspects.", 
            "dur": "3.282", 
            "start": "578.262"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The officer approached the car,", 
            "dur": "1.506", 
            "start": "581.544"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and he shined his flashlight\non the driver.", 
            "dur": "2.545", 
            "start": "583.05"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Then on my brother in the front seat,\nand then on me.", 
            "dur": "3.539", 
            "start": "585.595"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And his eyes opened wide, and he said,", 
            "dur": "2.602", 
            "start": "589.134"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Where have I seen your face before?&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.639", 
            "start": "591.736"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "2.088", 
            "start": "594.375"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I said, &quot;In the front seat.&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.152", 
            "start": "596.463"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "2.718", 
            "start": "600.439"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But that made no sense to him whatsoever.", 
            "dur": "2.353", 
            "start": "603.157"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So now he thought I was on drugs.", 
            "dur": "2.119", 
            "start": "605.51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.381", 
            "start": "607.629"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So he drags me out of the car,\nhe searches me,", 
            "dur": "2.403", 
            "start": "609.01"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "he marches me over to the police car,", 
            "dur": "2.19", 
            "start": "611.413"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and only when he verified\nI don&#39;t have a police record,", 
            "dur": "3.31", 
            "start": "613.603"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "could I show him I had a twin\nin the front seat.", 
            "dur": "3.928", 
            "start": "616.913"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But even as we were driving away,\nyou could see by the look on his face,", 
            "dur": "3.83", 
            "start": "620.931"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "he was convinced\nI was getting away with something.", 
            "dur": "3.493", 
            "start": "624.761"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Our mind is hard to change\nonce we become convinced.", 
            "dur": "3.95", 
            "start": "629.625"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So it might be very natural to feel\ndemoralized and defeated after you fail.", 
            "dur": "4.95", 
            "start": "633.575"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But you cannot allow yourself\nto become convinced you can&#39;t succeed.", 
            "dur": "3.737", 
            "start": "638.714"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You have to fight\nfeelings of helplessness.", 
            "dur": "2.876", 
            "start": "643.161"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You have to gain control\nover the situation,", 
            "dur": "3.002", 
            "start": "646.037"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you have to break this kind\nof negative cycle before it begins.", 
            "dur": "4.059", 
            "start": "649.073"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[Stop emotional bleeding]", 
            "dur": "2.094", 
            "start": "653.134"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Our minds and our feelings,", 
            "dur": "2.143", 
            "start": "655.228"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they are not the trustworthy friends\nwe thought they were.", 
            "dur": "3.688", 
            "start": "657.371"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They are more like a really moody friend,", 
            "dur": "2.804", 
            "start": "661.059"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "who can be totally supportive one minute,\nand really unpleasant the next.", 
            "dur": "5.164", 
            "start": "663.863"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I once worked with this woman", 
            "dur": "1.988", 
            "start": "669.027"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "who after 20 years of marriage\nand an extremely ugly divorce,", 
            "dur": "3.821", 
            "start": "671.015"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "was finally ready for her first date.", 
            "dur": "2.547", 
            "start": "674.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "She had met this guy online,\nhe seemed nice and successful,", 
            "dur": "4.197", 
            "start": "677.383"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and most importantly,\nhe seemed really into her.", 
            "dur": "3.126", 
            "start": "681.58"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So she was very excited,\nand she bought a new dress,", 
            "dur": "3.026", 
            "start": "685.052"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and they met at an upscale\nNew York City bar for a drink.", 
            "dur": "3.8", 
            "start": "688.078"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Ten minutes into the date,\nthe man stands up and says,", 
            "dur": "3.917", 
            "start": "691.878"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;I&#39;m not interested&quot;, and walks out.", 
            "dur": "3.108", 
            "start": "695.795"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[Rejection]", 
            "dur": "1.964", 
            "start": "698.903"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Rejection is extremely painful.", 
            "dur": "2.656", 
            "start": "700.867"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The woman was so hurt,\nshe could&#39;t move.", 
            "dur": "2.332", 
            "start": "704.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All she could do is call a friend.", 
            "dur": "2.22", 
            "start": "706.442"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And here&#39;s what the friend said,\n&quot;Well, what do you expect,", 
            "dur": "4.514", 
            "start": "708.662"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you have big hips,\nyou have nothing interesting to say,", 
            "dur": "3.546", 
            "start": "713.176"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "why would a handsome,\nsuccessful man like that", 
            "dur": "2.961", 
            "start": "716.722"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "ever go out with a loser like you?&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.613", 
            "start": "719.683"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Shocking, right,\nthat a friend could be so cruel.", 
            "dur": "3.496", 
            "start": "723.743"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But it would be much less shocking", 
            "dur": "2.508", 
            "start": "727.239"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if I told you it wasn&#39;t\nthe friend who said that.", 
            "dur": "2.904", 
            "start": "729.747"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s what the woman said to herself.", 
            "dur": "2.877", 
            "start": "732.651"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that&#39;s something we all do.", 
            "dur": "2.625", 
            "start": "735.528"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Especially after a rejection.", 
            "dur": "2.047", 
            "start": "738.153"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We all start thinking of all our faults\nand all our shortcomings", 
            "dur": "3.403", 
            "start": "740.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what we wish we were,\nwhat we wish we weren&#39;t,", 
            "dur": "2.348", 
            "start": "743.603"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we call ourselves names.", 
            "dur": "1.487", 
            "start": "745.951"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Maybe not as harshly,\nbut we all do it.", 
            "dur": "2.371", 
            "start": "747.438"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s interesting that we do, because\nour self-esteem is already hurting.", 
            "dur": "4.58", 
            "start": "749.839"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Why would we want to go\nand damage it even further?", 
            "dur": "3.428", 
            "start": "754.953"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We wouldn&#39;t make a physical injury\nworse on purpose.", 
            "dur": "2.636", 
            "start": "758.381"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You wouldn&#39;t get a cut on your arm\nand decide,", 
            "dur": "2.506", 
            "start": "761.017"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Oh, I know, I am going to take a knife\nand see how much deeper I can make it.&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.886", 
            "start": "763.523"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But we do that with psychological injuries\nall the time.", 
            "dur": "3.534", 
            "start": "767.409"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Why? Because of poor emotional hygiene.", 
            "dur": "3.225", 
            "start": "770.943"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because we don&#39;t prioritize\nour psychological health.", 
            "dur": "3.451", 
            "start": "774.168"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We know from dozens of studies,", 
            "dur": "1.777", 
            "start": "777.619"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that when your self-esteem is lower,", 
            "dur": "1.983", 
            "start": "779.396"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you are more vulnerable\nto stress and to anxiety,", 
            "dur": "3.094", 
            "start": "781.379"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that failures and rejections hurt more,", 
            "dur": "3.157", 
            "start": "784.473"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and it takes longer to recover from them.", 
            "dur": "2.718", 
            "start": "787.63"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So when you get rejected,\nthe first thing you should be doing", 
            "dur": "3.086", 
            "start": "790.348"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is to revive your self-esteem,", 
            "dur": "2.477", 
            "start": "793.434"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "not join Fight Club\nand beat it into a pulp.", 
            "dur": "3.09", 
            "start": "795.911"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When you are in emotional pain,", 
            "dur": "2.451", 
            "start": "800.005"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "treat yourself with the same compassion", 
            "dur": "2.84", 
            "start": "802.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you would expect from a truly good friend.", 
            "dur": "2.915", 
            "start": "805.296"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[Protect your self-esteem]", 
            "dur": "2.146", 
            "start": "808.211"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We have to catch our unhealthy\npsychological habits and change them.", 
            "dur": "3.685", 
            "start": "810.357"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "One of the unhealthiest and most common\nis called rumination.", 
            "dur": "4.252", 
            "start": "814.128"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "To ruminate, means to chew over.", 
            "dur": "2.391", 
            "start": "819.108"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s when your boss yells at you,", 
            "dur": "2.141", 
            "start": "821.499"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or your professor makes you\nfeel stupid in class,", 
            "dur": "2.882", 
            "start": "823.64"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or you have a big fight with a friend,", 
            "dur": "2.591", 
            "start": "826.522"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you just can&#39;t stop replaying\nthe scene in your head for days,", 
            "dur": "3.816", 
            "start": "829.113"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "sometimes for weeks on end.", 
            "dur": "2.143", 
            "start": "832.929"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now ruminating\nabout upsetting events in this way", 
            "dur": "3.322", 
            "start": "835.072"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "can easily become a habit,\nand it&#39;s a very costly one.", 
            "dur": "3.471", 
            "start": "838.394"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because by spending so much time", 
            "dur": "2.076", 
            "start": "841.865"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "focused on upsetting\nand negative thoughts,", 
            "dur": "2.874", 
            "start": "843.941"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you are actually putting yourself\nat significant risk for developing", 
            "dur": "3.737", 
            "start": "846.815"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "clinical depression, alcoholism,", 
            "dur": "3.051", 
            "start": "850.58"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "eating disorders\nand even cardiovascular disease.", 
            "dur": "3.45", 
            "start": "853.631"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The problem is, the urge to ruminate", 
            "dur": "3.256", 
            "start": "857.081"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "can feel really strong, really important,\nso it&#39;s a difficult habit to stop.", 
            "dur": "4.092", 
            "start": "860.337"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I know this for a fact.", 
            "dur": "2.064", 
            "start": "865.115"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because little over a year ago,\nI developed the habit myself.", 
            "dur": "4.121", 
            "start": "867.179"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You see my twin brother was diagnosed", 
            "dur": "2.828", 
            "start": "871.3"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with stage III non-Hodgkin&#39;s lymphoma.", 
            "dur": "3.323", 
            "start": "874.128"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "His cancer was extremly aggressive,", 
            "dur": "2.335", 
            "start": "877.451"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "he had visible tumors all over his body.", 
            "dur": "3.251", 
            "start": "879.786"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And he had to start a harsh course\nof chemotherapy.", 
            "dur": "3.724", 
            "start": "883.631"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I couldn&#39;t stop thinking\nabout what he was going through,", 
            "dur": "4.083", 
            "start": "888.494"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I could&#39;t stop thinking\nabout how much he was suffering.", 
            "dur": "3.292", 
            "start": "892.762"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Even though he never complained, not once.", 
            "dur": "3.53", 
            "start": "897.255"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He had this incredibly positive attitude.", 
            "dur": "2.748", 
            "start": "901.072"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "His psychological health was amazing.", 
            "dur": "3.098", 
            "start": "903.82"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was physically healthy,\nbut psychologically I was a mess.", 
            "dur": "4.427", 
            "start": "906.918"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I knew what to do.", 
            "dur": "1.549", 
            "start": "912.014"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Studies tell us\nthat even a two minute distraction", 
            "dur": "3.37", 
            "start": "913.563"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is sufficient to break the urge\nto ruminate in that moment.", 
            "dur": "3.934", 
            "start": "916.933"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And so each time I had a worrying,\nupsetting, negative thought,", 
            "dur": "3.25", 
            "start": "921.055"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I forced myself to concentrate\non something else until the urge passed.", 
            "dur": "4.359", 
            "start": "924.305"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And within one week,\nmy whole outlook changed,", 
            "dur": "4.565", 
            "start": "928.698"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and became more positive\nand more hopeful.", 
            "dur": "2.988", 
            "start": "933.263"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[Battle negative thinking]", 
            "dur": "1.812", 
            "start": "936.693"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Nine weeks after he started chemotherapy,\nmy brother had a CAT scan,", 
            "dur": "4.144", 
            "start": "938.505"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I was by his side\nwhen he got the results.", 
            "dur": "3.136", 
            "start": "942.744"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All the tumors were gone.", 
            "dur": "2.617", 
            "start": "945.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He still had three more rounds\nof chemotherapy to go.", 
            "dur": "3.157", 
            "start": "948.497"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But we knew he would recover. \n", 
            "dur": "2.077", 
            "start": "951.654"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This picture was taken two weeks ago.", 
            "dur": "3.41", 
            "start": "954.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "By taking action when you&#39;re lonely,", 
            "dur": "2.905", 
            "start": "960.682"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "by changing your responses to failure,", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "963.595"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "by protecting yourself-esteem,", 
            "dur": "2.562", 
            "start": "966.595"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "by battling negative thinking,", 
            "dur": "2.492", 
            "start": "969.157"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you won&#39;t just heal\nyour psychological wounds,", 
            "dur": "3.308", 
            "start": "971.649"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you will build emotional resilience,\nyou will thrive.", 
            "dur": "3.217", 
            "start": "974.957"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A hundred years ago,\npeople began practicing personal hygiene.", 
            "dur": "4.031", 
            "start": "979.673"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And life expectancy rates rose\nby over fifty percent", 
            "dur": "4.655", 
            "start": "983.768"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in just a matter of decades.", 
            "dur": "2.161", 
            "start": "988.423"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I believe our quality of life\ncould rise just as dramatically", 
            "dur": "3.884", 
            "start": "990.584"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if we all began practicing\nemotional hygiene.", 
            "dur": "3.804", 
            "start": "994.468"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Can you imagine,\nwhat the world would be like", 
            "dur": "3.341", 
            "start": "998.841"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if everyone was psychologically healthier?", 
            "dur": "2.294", 
            "start": "1002.182"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If there were less loneliness,\nand less depression?", 
            "dur": "3.951", 
            "start": "1004.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If people knew how to overcome failure?", 
            "dur": "2.672", 
            "start": "1008.427"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If they felt better about themselves,\nand more empowered?", 
            "dur": "3.314", 
            "start": "1011.099"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if they were happier, and more fulfilled?", 
            "dur": "3.239", 
            "start": "1014.413"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I can, because that&#39;s the world\nI want to live in,", 
            "dur": "3.174", 
            "start": "1017.652"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that&#39;s the world\nmy brother wants to live in as well.", 
            "dur": "3.795", 
            "start": "1022.226"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you just become informed,\nand change a few simple habits,", 
            "dur": "4.633", 
            "start": "1026.021"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "well that&#39;s the world we can all live in.", 
            "dur": "3.698", 
            "start": "1030.654"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Thank you very much.", 
            "dur": "1.742", 
            "start": "1035.071"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Applause)", 
            "dur": "2.755", 
            "start": "1036.813"
        }
    ], 
